    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>First globally declare </p>\n\n<p><strong><code>Context mContext;</code></strong> </p>\n\n<p>pass context with the constructor, by modifying it.</p>\n\n<pre><code>public FeedAdapter(List&lt;Post&gt; myDataset, Context context) {\n    mDataset = myDataset;\n    this.mContext = context;\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>then use the <code>mContext</code> whereever you need it</p>\n"
