      "creation_date" : 1513894719,
      "post_id" : 34873343,
      "comment_id" : 82836130,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "If the adapter is attached to a RecyclerView then that context is guaranteed to be needed anyway. If you might unattach the adapter, then it&#39;s still fine unless for some reason you hold a strong reference to this adapter after it&#39;s been detached, in which case you should clear out the cached context, there is a method like <code>onDetachedFromRecyclerView</code> or something."
    } ],
