    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>You can use like this <strong>view.getContext()</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Example</strong></p>\n\n<pre><code>holder.tv_room_name.setOnClickListener(new View.OnClickListener() {\n        @Override\n        public void onClick(View v) {\n\n            Toast.makeText(v.getContext(), \"\", Toast.LENGTH_SHORT).show();\n\n\n        }\n    });\n</code></pre>\n"
