    "creation_date" : 1545340508,
    "answer_id" : 53876151,
    "question_id" : 32136973,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>You can define:</p>\n\n<pre><code>Context ctx; \n</code></pre>\n\n<p>And on <code>onCreate</code> initialise <code>ctx</code> to: </p>\n\n<pre><code>ctx=parent.getContext(); \n</code></pre>\n\n<p>Note: Parent is a ViewGroup.</p>\n"
